  "body": "<p>One of the best parts about working with Amy these past couple of years has been her willingness to let me photograph so much of her life. Today I thought it would be fun to share some of favorite moments that we've been able to capture thus far! </p><p><strong>We documented her ever-growing bump:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"13a-amy.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/31316c1201e195b5.jpg?v=1782535447\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"13b-amy1.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/7c5eeeb5c5cb00d7.jpg?v=1782535450\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13c-amy15.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/2ffc989a4c8c7d8c.jpg?v=1782535452\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Which later turned into her ever-growing baby Jack:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"13d-amy8.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/5ab886f4cfef78db.jpg?v=1782535455\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13e-amy3.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/13a6457703fbe725.jpg?v=1782535458\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13f-amy2.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/54c712a57f6d0605.jpg?v=1782535461\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p><strong>We rounded up the family for a few impromptu portraits:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"13g-amy4.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/a12a0ec0e48ed0f9.jpg?v=1782535464\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13h-amy5.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/28da96e39e602469.jpg?v=1782535467\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13i-amy6.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/41cc8b4710068aa4.jpg?v=1782535470\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p><strong>We wandered around town:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"13j-amy10.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/ba5227ed03906b14.jpg?v=1782535472\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13k-amy_dogs.gif\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/3bbe1649f2a4f940.gif?v=1782535476\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13l-lundeens_2.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/f661157bd14d7cb9.jpg?v=1782535478\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p><strong>We hung out in her studio:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"13m-amy13.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/8efb6e310b15b06a.jpg?v=1782535481\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13n-amy12.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/5ef23beaa64c41da.jpg?v=1782535484\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13o-amy14.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/ac95afb035a857b8.jpg?v=1782535487\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p><strong>We then moved to </strong><strong>the house</strong><strong> for a snack break:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"13p-house_6-600x442.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/d63064bb6e0317d8.jpg?v=1782535489\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13q-jack_10-600x400.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/f8f814ee3b8264e9.jpg?v=1782535492\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"13r-house_1-600x441.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/0bb2a518ac45d6e1.jpg?v=1782535495\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p><strong>And every so often, we would even get a photo together:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/681365c457a698a7.jpg?v=1782535498\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p><strong>No matter where we are or what we're doing, Amy is always down for a photo op. <em>She's my kind of girl.</em></strong></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
}